THE PROJECT MAKES USE OF LINEAR AGRESSION TO TRY TO PREDICT THE SALARY OF 
A NEW EMPLOYEE IN A HUGE COMPANY. THE PROGRAM IS DIVIDED INTO THE FOLLOWING STEPS

STEP 1: IMPORT THE LIBRARIES (numpy, pandas, matplotlib, seaborn)
STEP 2: IMPORT THE DATASET (.csv) using the read_csv() from pandas
STEP 3: VISUALIZE THE DATA USING SEABORN
STEP 4: SPLIT THE DATA INTO TRAINING SETS AND TESTING SETS
STEP 5: FIT THE LINEAR REGRESSION TO THE TRAINING SET 
STEP 6: TEST THE MODEL 
STEP 7: VISUALIZE THE TEST RESULTS
STEP 8: VISUALIZE THE TRAINING RESULTS
STEP 9: CALCULATE THE RESIDUALS

HAPPY CODING!!!!!
